- "Racked up the most points and goals" refers to the highest total points and goals scored in the 2022 season;
- "Team they are joining" refers to the team to which the player is transferring.

- "Top 3 teams" refers to teams ranked highest based on points and goal difference;
- "Most experienced coach" refers to the coach with the highest number of years of experience;
- "Top-scoring player" refers to the player with the highest total points (goals + assists) in their team.

